text: Serenay is a Turkish feminine name. Notable people with the name include: *Serenay Aktaş (born 1993), Turkish former women's footballer, and television and film actress *Serenay Öziri (born 1994), Turkish women's footballer *Serenay Sarıkaya (born 1991), Turkish actress and model ==See also== * Serena (disambiguation)
title: Serenay
